${statement}: SELECT o1/name/value, o2/name/value FROM EHR e CONTAINS (OBSERVATION o1[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0] AND OBSERVATION o2[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.blood_pressure.v2])
SELECT o1/name/value, o2/name/value FROM EHR e CONTAINS (OBSERVATION o1[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0] OR OBSERVATION o2[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.blood_pressure.v2])

SELECT s1/name/value, o1/name/value, s2/name/value, o2/name/value FROM EHR e CONTAINS ((SECTION s1[openEHR-EHR-SECTION.conformance_section.v0] CONTAINS OBSERVATION o1[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0]) OR (SECTION s2[openEHR-EHR-SECTION.adhoc.v1,'Section 1'] CONTAINS OBSERVATION o2[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0]))

SELECT s1/name/value, o1/name/value, o2/name/value FROM SECTION s1 CONTAINS (OBSERVATION o1[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0] AND OBSERVATION o2[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.blood_pressure.v2])

SELECT s1/name/value, o1/name/value, c/name/value, o2/name/value, o3/name/value FROM EHR e CONTAINS (SECTION s1 CONTAINS ((OBSERVATION o1 CONTAINS CLUSTER c) AND OBSERVATION o2[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.blood_pressure.v2]) OR OBSERVATION o3[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.conformance_observation.v0])
